{"tid":1701226,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全城悲憤 悼梓樂 要真相 「我們代你走下去」","createTime":"2019-11-09T02:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T02:54:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a06e096490c7c970ee9f9898820371a2dd2a8c63","tid":1701226,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191109/KGR6SNZ4FJPO6HT3BRN7HAQRSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191109%2FKGR6SNZ4FJPO6HT3BRN7HAQRSU%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOID442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=ead8ffa9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191109%2FKGR6SNZ4FJPO6HT3BRN7HAQRSU%2F&h=800cadee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191109/KGR6SNZ4FJPO6HT3BRN7HAQRSU/</a><br />\n<br />\n全城悲憤 悼梓樂 要真相<br />\n「我們代你走下去」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】周一在將軍澳尚德邨停車場離奇墮樓的22歲科技大學男生周梓樂留院四日，昨晨終告不治，不幸成為香港反送中引發逆權抗暴運動中，首位在示威現場傷重犧牲的抗爭者。梓樂死訊公佈後，全港各區悼念人潮不絕，為年輕生命消逝痛哭，為真相未明悲憤，各界包括科大校長史維均要求獨立調查事件。至深夜多區悼念活動再度演變成警民激烈衝突，油麻地更有警員向天開真槍，至凌晨警方已拘捕多人。<br />\n<br />\n記者：姜偉康 溫瑞麟 溫文學<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：畢業禮接噩耗 科大生洶湧<br />\n<br />\n星期日深夜防暴警察在將軍澳與示威者攻防，並施放催淚彈，周梓樂星期一凌晨被發現由尚德邨停車場墮樓，腦部及盆骨重創，昏迷送院後一直與死神搏鬥，但兩次手術失敗，減腦壓及安裝心塞輔助器均告無效，腦部腫脹，電解質等失衡嚴重，導致心律不正，留醫至第五日的昨早8時09分，因心臟停頓死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/75TeZtzWEgWFsEDNLgAlxwIhdq0=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/AHORNDLET2MQ4ZOAPJXTEJ4CRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F75TeZtzWEgWFsEDNLgAlxwIhdq0%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FAHORNDLET2MQ4ZOAPJXTEJ4CRU.jpg&h=9a16ca9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【將軍澳】逾千名市民排隊到周梓樂墮斃的尚德邨停車場致哀。謝榮耀攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/OIxHjzFYDv8DjHs4pnFdmxvsHI0=/802x950/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/P2YIZRZPMUW367S2TB24UG4S7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FOIxHjzFYDv8DjHs4pnFdmxvsHI0%3D%2F802x950%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FP2YIZRZPMUW367S2TB24UG4S7Q.jpg&h=0f1294bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周梓樂<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/nzkwhJJdqQLAJKdli5Csw8rcjwU=/802x447/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/RZIBRXAUZSK7KGHEHWZWTB6JZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FnzkwhJJdqQLAJKdli5Csw8rcjwU%3D%2F802x447%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FRZIBRXAUZSK7KGHEHWZWTB6JZU.jpg&h=6afdc65a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【沙 田】近500人在新城市廣場聚集悼念。溫文學攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/tT69vKqe6aVBNaWdnH06gS7Cz34=/802x506/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/TXG4YXPVTWSOFG45A72H46BUFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FtT69vKqe6aVBNaWdnH06gS7Cz34%3D%2F802x506%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FTXG4YXPVTWSOFG45A72H46BUFA.jpg&h=fe1244f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【觀 塘】中學生在海濱公園集會，以燭光砌出「梓樂」兩字。黃雲慶攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/CWEe7luVbh56yB7WQxchQW96TSM=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/J3ZOZGZ7IO7DAZV4DEGSFMWPEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FCWEe7luVbh56yB7WQxchQW96TSM%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FJ3ZOZGZ7IO7DAZV4DEGSFMWPEU.jpg&h=c4dbc0b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中 環】有市民在中環碼頭為死者落淚。王子俊攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尚德邨千人排隊致哀<br />\n<br />\n周同學的姑媽及外公早上9時半步出深切治療病房後，雙眼通紅招手叫數名同學入內，向梓樂作最後告別。科大副學生事務長林惟良及計算機科學及工程學系署理系主任楊瓞仁到場慰問家屬，其後校長史維在畢業禮中向同學公佈消息。科大校園氣氛哀傷，有學生掛出「周梓樂我們會代你走下去」的橫幅。<br />\n<br />\n繼7.21元朗恐襲、8.31速龍太子站打人後，梓樂墮樓案疑點重重，警方又被指延誤救援，令香港人對警隊憤怒進一步升溫。周同學死訊傳出後，中環中午大批市民自發舉行快閃悼念集會，科大學生會臨時會長黎煒進在醫院代家屬發言，感激全港市民多日來的支持，呼籲全港市民下午1點放下手頭工作，一同為死者默哀。有市民喊出「香港人，報仇!」的口號，取代以往的「香港人，加油!」或近期的「香港人，反抗!」<br />\n<br />\n理工大學學生會中午在校內舉行悼念儀式，約300名師生和教職員出席，並戴上黑口罩和繫上黑絲帶默哀。有學生許諾：「未來前路我願代你走下去」；也有學生促設第三方獨立調查死因，「一定唔可以靠香港警察，信唔過」。<br />\n<br />\n網民其後發起晚上7時45分在將軍澳、沙田、屯門、元朗、中環、尖沙嘴、銅鑼灣、香港仔、荃灣等27個地點集合，舉行追思集會，至8時正一同為死者默哀數分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n當中，以事發現場尚德邨停車場聚集人數最多，黑衣人潮從將軍澳站絡繹不絕，一度超過千人排隊致哀，人龍延後至尚德廣場。巿民攜着鮮花及大大小小的心意memo紙，又在牆上劃出「周梓樂同學主懷安息」心意板，讓到場市民留下悼念字句。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/QBHxwLN0vZzwk401ixMag19mwdo=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/O75AH4TC3U7AG4NLKDWMGNRMYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FQBHxwLN0vZzwk401ixMag19mwdo%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FO75AH4TC3U7AG4NLKDWMGNRMYU.jpg&h=57949135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批市民在尚德邨停車場聚集，並掛起「警謊殺人」直幡。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/l687VY18ezuhEEGYchcHDK3Goyo=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/UBQASBZ3UU4466SZPYAA5RX3MY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fl687VY18ezuhEEGYchcHDK3Goyo%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FUBQASBZ3UU4466SZPYAA5RX3MY.jpg&h=1de67e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環碼頭有市民舉起早前離奇死亡的陳彥霖及周梓樂的畫像悼念。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/PnHiq5KuUHXj1OwjR9ERCbmQtwg=/802x692/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ETATU7S55KCGWSXROSWI222BGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FPnHiq5KuUHXj1OwjR9ERCbmQtwg%3D%2F802x692%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FETATU7S55KCGWSXROSWI222BGA.jpg&h=534de4e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民在尚德邨停車場摺紙鶴表達心意。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/UexiW2NLeP1aNbtqBb18c-BWKHU=/802x692/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/2S4I6GR4R6I5IP2GDEI5EPWEUI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FUexiW2NLeP1aNbtqBb18c-BWKHU%3D%2F802x692%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F2S4I6GR4R6I5IP2GDEI5EPWEUI.jpg&h=2c3f8f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尚德邨停車場有市民點起蠟燭悼念死者。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民：港人已不能退縮<br />\n<br />\n大部份巿民不發一言，向着周同學墮下地點擺放鮮花，欄河掛着一幅「全民集氣 天佑梓樂」黑底白字橫額，有人燃點白燭，現場傳出啜泣聲，當有人嘗試高叫口號時，被人連聲「噓噓」叫停，揚言「畀大家靜一靜！」全都克制沒有再叫口號。有巿民則在停車場牆上貼文宣包括「警謊殺人」巨型直幡，以及「NEVER FORGET, NEVER FORGIVE」等橫額。<br />\n<br />\n前來尚德邨停車場悼念的李先生表示，反送中運動經歷五個多月，政府對港人五大訴求只是撤回修例，目前民眾首要希望是解散警隊，因警方濫捕造成大好青年喪命，港人已經不能退縮，「唔止反抗同報仇，要贏落去，先對得住已經犧牲嘅手足」。他續指，每次警民衝突過後，警方為警暴開脫，不願意承擔責任，導致巿民不再相信警方，「唔係我哋選擇唔相信，而係佢哋誠信破產，無法令人相信佢嘅講法。」<br />\n<br />\n另一名巿民Mason表示，周同學的離世，讓香港人憤怒及不捨，覺得「輸咗小朋友畀呢個政權」，而警方每次開記者會解釋，好快便被新證據推翻，變相「佢淨係講返自己嗰套說話」，抗爭者的新口號「香港人，報仇!」正正反映巿民對警方不公義的憤怒。"},{"pid":"73a6835503d2f848cb982d85196728edfb423f29","tid":1701226,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}